## Summary checklist (HandsOff)

- [ ] Test cases: written to `test_cases/Flows/<Flow>/` (or Objects); folder and .md files verified on disk; Flows/README.md updated.
- [ ] Playwright: spec created in `EnergoTS/tests/cursor/{JIRA_KEY}-*.spec.ts` (or equivalent); file verified on disk; **number of `test()` blocks equals total number of test cases (TC-1, TC-2, …) in the .md files in that folder** – full coverage, 1:1.
- [ ] Report: content is **only** Playwright test results (per test: what is verified, steps, result, failure reason).
- [ ] Slack: report built from **`Cursor-Project/config/Slack_report_template.md`**; full report sent **only** to **Tester** (DM) and **#ai-report** (channel_id **C0AK96S1D7X**); **never** to Assignee or anyone else; not a short summary.
- [ ] Agent questions: after report, collect questions from each participating agent (as needed); each question tagged with agent name; send questions after the report to the same recipients (Tester and #ai-report only).

Violation: repeat of the above problems is a workflow error; correct before considering HandsOff complete.
